315
0:34:10,518 --> 0:34:13,846
BATTERY CAGES


316
0:34:13,846 --> 0:34:23,43
Many lose their feathers and develop
sores from rubbing against the wire cage.


317
0:34:23,43 --> 0:34:28,43
Crowding prevents them from
