323
0:34:50,389 --> 0:34:56,124
SLAUGHTER


324
0:34:56,124 --> 0:35:30,709
"THE HANG PEN"
MOOREFIELD, WEST VIRGINIA


325
0:35:30,709 --> 0:35:35,756
Chickens and turkeys are
