672
1:13:13,744 --> 1:13:21,348
PART FIVE: SCIENCE


673
1:13:21,348 --> 1:13:23,798
VIVISECTION


674
1:13:23,798 --> 1:13:27,607
The term vivisection is used
to apply to all types of experiments


675
1:13:27,607 --> 1:13:34,182
